import { Box, Stack, Text, Button, Center  } from '@chakra-ui/react'

function App() {
  return (
    <Box justifyItems='center'>
      <Stack spacing={0} direction='column'>
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#81ecec'>
            <Button colorScheme="#81ecec" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large' w='100%' p='15vh'> #81ecec </Button>
          </Center >
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#74b9ff'>
            <Button colorScheme="#74b9ff" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large'  w='100%' p='15vh'> #74b9ff </Button>
          </Center >
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#a29bfe'>
            <Button colorScheme="#a29bfe" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large'  w='100%' p='15vh'> #a29bfe </Button>
          </Center > 
        </Stack>
        
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#00cec9'>
            <Button colorScheme="#00cec9" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large' w='100%' p='15vh'> #00cec9 </Button>
          </Center >
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#0984e3'>
            <Button colorScheme="#0984e3" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large'  w='100%' p='15vh'> #0984e3 </Button>
          </Center >
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#6c5ce7'>
            <Button colorScheme="#6c5ce7" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large'  w='100%' p='15vh'> #6c5ce7 </Button>
          </Center > 
        </Stack>

        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#fab1a0'>
            <Button colorScheme="#fab1a0" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large' w='100%' p='15vh'> #fab1a0 </Button>
          </Center >
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#ff7675'>
            <Button colorScheme="#ff7675" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large'  w='100%' p='15vh'> #ff7675 </Button>
          </Center >
          <Center  w="100%" backgroundColor='#a29bfe'>
            <Button colorScheme="#a29bfe" variant="link" color="white" fontSize='x-large'  w='100%' p='15vh'> #a29bfe </Button>
          </Center > 
        </Stack>
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default App;
